data.description: Come view this beautiful home: 2-story, 4bd/2.5 bath house on a cul-de-sac with a basement ready for your personal touch. The master is located on the main floor with 3 bedrooms on the second floor. This home features a 2-story foyer, formal dining, and upgraded kitchen with granite, under cabinet lighting, tile, and new soft-close cabinets. Kitchen opens to a 2-story family room with a wood-burning fireplace and tall 10 ft ceilings. The main floor has beautiful hardwood floors.
